Package com.example.qrcodeteam30.modelclass

Class QRCode

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.qrcodeteam30.modelclass.QRCode
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    public class QRCode
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    This model class represents a QR code and its properties Including username that the QR code belongs to, the content, the location, the date of taken The score, the reference to the list of comment on Firestore, the format (QR code/barcodes/...), the reference to the photo on Firestore
